      "body": "T14 projectivity foundation landed: P(n;S) + Serre O(m) + projective-with-L predicate; one C2 sorry; quotBoundedness deferred\n\nFour new files, full build green (8666 jobs). (1) ProjectiveSpace.lean: relative P(n;S) := pullback over Spec Z of Proj Z[X_i] (AffineSpace pattern, universe-polymorphic); gradeZeroRingEquiv (degree-0 part = Z, so Spec of it terminal); IsProper/IsSeparated on the structural morphism by base change from Mathlib Proj.toSpecZero; map/map_id/map_comp/isPullback_map \u2014 all AXIOM-CLEAN. (2) SerreTwist.lean: O(m) on Proj Z[X_i] glued from trivial bundles on D+(X_i) with transitions (X_i/X_j)^m via Scheme.Modules.glue; awayUnit/overlapUnit real; C1 (twistTransition_self) PROVED; the ONE sorry is twistTransition_cocycle (C2 triple-overlap transport, rank-1 analogue of bundleTransition_cocycle_transport) \u2014 everything mentioning serreTwist carries sorryAx through this single leaf. (3) ProjectiveMorphism.lean: Scheme.Hom.IsProjectiveWith pi L (closed immersion into P(Fin(d+1);S) over S with L iso i^*O(1); the I-0118 encoding (a)); isProper, comp_isClosedImmersion, baseChange all PROVED (complete proofs; axiom-taint only via the O(1) term inside the statement). (4) SerreFiniteness.lean: AlgebraicGeometry.sectionGradedModule_fg STATED honestly (Noetherian section ring + Module.Finite of the section module + componentwise FiniteDimensional; hypothesis = IsProjectiveWith) as the named deep leaf; blueprint node flipped to statement-leanok with the very-ample hypothesis. CAVEATS: (a) glue/glueLift are universe-monomorphic at Scheme.GlueData.{0} (GlueDescent.lean:934), so serreTwist/predicate/stability live at Scheme.{0}; the eventual QuotScheme restatement will specialize to Scheme.{0} unless the glue engine is generalized. (b) TODO.quotBoundedness (lem:quot_boundedness) NOT stated this session: a faithful statement needs CM-regularity + R^i pi_* twist vocabulary that does not exist yet; stating it loosely would repeat the I-0118 tra